OL,3,CMan arrested after 12-hour stand-off
OL,4,Cwith armed police and negotiators
OL,6,FPolice have made an arrest after
OL,7,Freports a man had barricaded himself
OL,8,Fin a home in a 12-hour standoff.
OL,10,FWest Midlands Police were called to
OL,11,FWestwood Road in Perry Barr,
OL,12,FBirmingham, late on Wednesday, 8 July.
OL,13,FOfficers cordoned off an area around
OL,14,Fthe junction with Tame Road.
OL,16,FA 20-year-old man has now been
OL,17,Farrested on suspicion of making
OL,18,Fthreats with a blade and possession of
OL,19,Fclass A drugs.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
