PN,34302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1783693094
OL,3,CMan arrested after 12-hour stand-off
OL,4,Cwith armed police and negotiators
OL,6,FThe force said at 5pm on Thursday that
OL,7,F"the matter was brought to a safe
OL,8,Fconclusion".
OL,10,FThey added: "He (the arrested man)
OL,11,Fremains in police custody. We want to
OL,12,Fthank the local community for their
OL,13,Fpatience."
OL,15,FOfficers said earlier they did not
OL,16,Fbelieve anyone else was inside and the
OL,17,Fsafety of the man is their priority.
OL,19,FArmed police and negotiators were also
OL,20,Fin attendance.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/3
