PN,34303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1783693094
OL,3,CMan arrested after 12-hour stand-off
OL,4,Cwith armed police and negotiators
OL,6,FWest Midlands Ambulance Service, who
OL,7,Fwere called to the scene, said it
OL,8,Finvolved a "police incident at a
OL,9,Fprivate address".
OL,11,FA white police van was seen inside the
OL,12,Fcordon. A police helicopter and drones
OL,13,Fhave also been seen overhead.
